title: Annabelle Wallis
itunes:title: Annabelle Wallis
description:
Actress Annabelle Wallis [Silent Night, The Mummy, Malignant, The Tudors, Peaky Blinders] talks with Anna about her latest film, the dark comedy Silent Night, growing up in Portugal, the idea of prince charming, gaslighting, taking risks, the thrill of auditioning, and more.


Today’s Unqualified segment begins with a call from Martyn, who finds himself in an on-again, off-again relationship and questions whether he should keep trying to make it work. The second call is with Travis, who wonders if he has a moral obligation to include his wheelchair in his dating app photos.


If you’re in need of unqualified relationship advice, please write to us at bit.ly/ASKANNA


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
